<br>
The centaur approached her,his eyes scanning her taking note to the bandage on her right arm,and the dried blood that was around her left shoulder.Wounds from the battle in Scynthia.Kala growled low and charged the centaur.Just as he swung his sword toward her head,she ducked,and rolled to the side.Before the centaur had time to face her,she plundged her sword into his gut as deep as it would go.The centaur groaned in pain,and swung his sword around again trying to hit her before he fell,but she dodged in time,and pulled her sword from his gut.He soon fell limp and died.<br>
<br>
After the centaur had fallen,She looked at the bandages on her right arm,her arm had begun to bleed again,and most likely need stitches,and eventually the arrow head that was still lodged in her left shoulder would have to be removed,but now wasnt the time.She winced slightly from the pain,then growled in anger as she ran back into the battle........ <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showMessage?topicID=29.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showMessage?topicID=25.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.threadControl?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select nam